            "currentCldrName": "Lady Beetle",
            "description": "<p>A ladybug (ladybird, lady beetle), a <a href=\"/beetle/\">beetle</a> with a round, red shell with black spots. Generally depicted as a <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coccinella_septempunctata\">seven-</a> or <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coccinella_novemnotata\">nine-spotted</a> ladybug shown from above on its six legs, with <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antenna\">antennae</a> and its&nbsp;distinctively red-and-black, halved shell.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>May be used a symbol of good luck.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Facebook&rsquo;s ladybug is shown on its legs facing forward.</p>",
